data.description: Beautiful, fully updated 3 Bed 1 & 1/2 Bath Brick Ranch. New laminate floors throughout the home for easy maintenance. All stainless steel 2021 kitchen appliances. Granite counter tops, under counter kit sink., large subway tile back splash, new lighting, fully-updated bathrooms. Beautifully finished open basement. Fenced in backyard with large patio. Everything has been finished and ready for you to enjoy as your very own!
